4.go to console on firebase
5.run the bellow comments in your flurtter terminal (one by one order)
  1.flutter clean
  2.flutter pub get
  3.flutter init
  4.firebase logout
  5.firebase login (login with email allow )

//CRM Changes
1.go to constant.dart file in lib, change the details for your Company like logo
2.open login.dart in lib and goto the Welcome() function and check a 3rd function to add or rmove a holidays in this list
3.run the Welcome() function in login page (Welcome function is add your login details and update Crm start dater and holidays (only sunday is pre defined)
4.if you run a welcome function once then remove the function
5.login with bellow username and password
 username:Admin
 password:Admin@123

6.go to employee page and add employees
7.only HR and Admin have permission to add employee

